to insert map on page you need to  add on it a "Custom liquid" section on template and set the Liquid code field with the value like this

{%- render 'g-map-insert' -%}
{%- render 'g-map-pract-pins' -%}
{%- render 'g-map-init' -%}

where between insert and init you can put more than one pins. 
